astically reduced (precision can be increased) by requiring that multiple scan-lines in the input scan to the same result."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, this stronger condition can lead to missed barcodes (lower recall)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Confirmation is avoided for barcode types, which are by design resistant to false positives, (e.g. Code128) to maximize recall."}],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk\/sbsdkonedconfirmationmode","title":"SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/SBSDKBarcodeFormatDataBarConfiguration":{"abstract":[{"text":"GS1 DataBar barcode configuration. Add to scanner configuration to scan GS1 DataBar-14, GS1 DataBar-14 Truncated, GS1 DataBar-14 Stacked and GS1 DataBar-14 Stacked Omnidirectional barcodes.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKBarcodeFormatDataBarConfiguration","type":"topic","title":"SBSDKBarcodeFormatDataBarConfiguration","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SBSDKBarcodeFormatDataBarConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk\/sbsdkbarcodeformatdatabarconfiguration","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SBSDKBarcodeFormatDataBarConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol"}},"variantOverrides":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"patch":[{"op":"replace","value":"SBSDKGS1Handling","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeSc